Description: Fragmentary papyrus, with two columns of Demotic in horizontal lines (8 lines, and 6 lines, with 2 shorter entries below). On the verso are three columns (witness lists) with 10 lines, 2 lines, 8 lines.
Bibliographic references: Trismegistos / An interdisciplinary portal of papyrological and epigraphic resources (380609) (http://www.trismegistos.org/text/380609)
